Additionally, Asoma includes a full upper and lowercase character set, lining figures, math characters, punctuation, 5 distinct weights and support for Western European, Central European, South Eastern European and South American scripts.

This makes Asoma a great option for horror film titles. For some reason, it also works surprisingly well on packaging for black beans.
